{
  "stem": "1550.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in Kenya, we stayed for about two weeks, and then we left from there with another ship for the Middle East.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, that was now in the spring of 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Jewish Brigade Group at that time was in Italy, was fighting in Italy as part of the Eighth Army somewhere in Italy north of Rome, somewhere near Bologna.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But, of course, we had to go to-- to Egypt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Near the Suez Canal zone, there was the-- the Jewish Brigade Group [? that ?] depot and training center.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we arrived there in the Middle East in the- in the Suez Canal zone somewhere in March.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we went into-- into-- into basic-- what is called basic training.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went through that basic training, which takes about two or three months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, by that time this was already in May of 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And on May 8 of 1945-- I think, May 8, I think it was-- there war came to an end.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Germany surrendered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Shortly thereafter, the British government decided that the people in Mauritius were allowed to go after all, if they wanted to, to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In other words, anyone who was in the camp of Mauritians had a choice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They had a choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Either they could go back to-- go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Or, if they wanted, they could go back to the country where they came from.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In other words, some people decided to go back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was, for instance, in Mauritius, a group of about 30 or 40 Jewish communists.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "These people were more communist than Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They had never known, even, that they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But under the Hitler laws, they-- they-- suddenly discovered themselves as Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But they were-- they were communists.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
